(1) This Python script takes the 2015 Quarterbacks information from www.fantasypros.com (Fantasy Football Leaders).

It doest the following:
	a. Parses the page and load the information into a Pandas dataframe.
	b. Display the page in a tabulated form.
	c. Use the matplotlib to generate the bargraph on the data we have collected.
	
(0) Project dependencies:
This project needs some external Python packages. Please run the following command 
to install these Python packages before run the script

	pip install requests
	pip install pandas
	pip install beautifulsoup4
	pip install matplotlib
	
(2) To run this program:

	python poic.py 

